{"word":"H4142 - מוּסַבָּה - mûwçabbâh - moo-sab-baw' - Being changed","slug":"H4142","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מוּסַבָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mûwçabbâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>moo-sab-baw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Being changed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E1;&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E1;&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05D4; - mu&#x0302;sabba&#x0302;h  mu&#x0302;sabba&#x0302;h</b> - <i>moo-sab-baw', moo-sab-baw'</i><p/>Feminine of <a href=\"#/H4141\">H4141</a>; a <i>reversal</i>, that is, the <i>backside</i> (of a gem), <i>fold</i> (of a double leaved door), <i>transmutation</i> (of a name): - being changed, inclosed, be set, turning."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4036\">H4036</a>, <a href=\"#/H4141\">H4141</a>, <a href=\"#/H4524\">H4524</a>, <a href=\"#/H5252\">H5252</a>, <a href=\"#/H5437\">H5437</a>, <a href=\"#/H5438\">H5438</a>, <a href=\"#/H5439\">H5439</a>"}]}